User Data = To edit user data first stop the ec2 instance and edit user data.


You can attach detach IAM Role to the EC2 instance while running.


aws is Using XEN Virtualization at the backend.


while creating a image we can change root volume properties except size(C.Q)
while creating a image we can also add additional volume 

if your ec2 instance root volume is not encrypted , while creating image root volume is also not encrypted and vice versa

while creating a image additional volume can be encrypted.
Deregister AMI = Deleting the AMI 
