#!/bin/bash

yum install httpd unzip -y 
service httpd start
chkconfig httpd on 
mkdir /var/www/html
sudo wget https://www.tooplate.com/zip-templates/2137_barista_cafe.zip 
sudo unzip 2127*
sudo mv 2137*/* /var/www/html



WAF is used to secure the application , WAF stop DDOS


==>How to generate SSL Certificate
	Got to ACM --> Request Certificate --> Select Request a public Certificate --> Next --> Provide Domain Name : Ex:*.boom.com --> click on the 		certificate and create record in R53. (Make sure you purchase the domain first and then create record)


